articles.author: Brooke Edwards
articles.title: Scrub: SpaceX scrubs launch of SES satellite from Cape Canaveral - Florida Today
articles.description: SpaceX decided to stand down from a Wednesday launch attempt of a European communications satellite. They'll try again Thursday.
articles.content:
And, it's another scrub.
SpaceX called off Wednesday's launch attempt of a Falcon 9 rocket carrying a European communications satellite well ahead of the planned 5:25 p.m. liftoff. The company said … [+2195 chars]
